        <updateDate>2009-01-13T19:48:03Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Volunteer Pilot Act - Exempts certain small passenger or cargo charitable flights with standard airworthiness certificates, provided certain conditions are met, from: (1) the requirement to obtain an air carrier or commercial operator certificate; and (2) drug and alcohol testing requirements.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
